data.text: @Oregonian The great decouple. This will boomerang to bite everyone, unfortunately. Not supporting Russia's invasion, however...U.S. Secretary of State James Baker’s famous “not one inch eastward” assurance about NATO expansion in his meeting with Soviet leader Mikhail Gorbachev
@Oregonian Damn all it took to cure covid was to get involved in a war that we have nothing to do with. Should have done this sooner
